description:
&lt;p&gt;Tudor Gate Surgery is looking to recruit a Salaried GP.  We are a recently refurbished surgery in the market town of Abergavenny on the edge of the Black Mountains and Brecon Beacons National Park. The town has good rail and road links and has easy commuting to Newport, Bristol and Cardiff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our clinical team comprises of 5 GP partners, 1 Salaried GP, 4 Nurses and 2 HCAs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Practice Information:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  List Size approx. 8700&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Vision Clinical System&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Dispensary service for rural patients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Training Practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Midwife, Health Visitor, Palliative Care Nurses, District Nurses, Practice HB Pharmacist and Counsellor linked to the practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  E/Services include:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Minor Surgery / Joint Injections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Family Planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  INR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Care Homes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Brief:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  6 weeks annual leave plus 1 week study leave&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  4 clinical sessions to be worked over 2 days &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  We will be offering an attractive sessional rate of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission statement is “To provide robust, effective, accessible healthcare services for the patients of Tudor Gate Surgery”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Embracing our core values of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;·         &lt;strong&gt;Openness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;·         &lt;strong&gt;Fairness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;·         &lt;strong&gt;Respect&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;·         &lt;strong&gt;Accountability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel you would like to know more about joining our team please email our Practice Manager – Sarah.Lapping@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We welcome informal visits beforehand.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
